<h3>게시판 상세 내용입니다</h3>
<p> ID : <%=@post.id%> </p>
<p> 작성자 : <%=@post.username%></p>
<p> 제목 : <%=@post.title%></p>
<p> 내용 : <%=@post.content%></p>
<p> 작성시간 : <%=@post.created_at%></p>

<hr />
<h4> 댓글을 입력해주세용</h4>
<form action="/post/add_comment">
<input type="text" name ="content" palceholder="댓글 입력해주셈"/>
<input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= @post.id %>">
<input type ="submit" />
</form>

<hr />

<% @post.comments.reverse.each_with_index do |comment, i|%>
<%=@post.comments.length- i%>번째 댓글 : <p><%= comment.content%> </p>
<% end%>
